    Determines how the TypeQualifier matches types

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      ANY_PROVIDER
      Matches any type providing the requested type, ignores any Named constraint on the type
      EXACT_TYPE
      Matches the exact named type only
